When will you come to your senses?

32
00:02:39,042 --> 00:02:41,311
I'm the only one who will care for you.

33
00:02:46,783 --> 00:02:48,251
You had virgin complex?
It happened long ago.

34
00:02:48,785 --> 00:02:49,986
What's wrong with you?

35
00:02:49,986 --> 00:02:51,488
I'm only doing it for fun that night.

36
00:02:52,022 --> 00:02:54,124
Just for fun, okay?

37
00:03:04,801 --> 00:03:06,669
Mr. Yi, someone's been
picking on Ai Di in a bar.

38
00:03:26,787 --> 00:03:29,790
You dyed your hair blonde
when studying abroad.

39
00:03:30,557 --> 00:03:32,426
Di Di.

40
00:03:32,426 --> 00:03:34,394
Don't call me that. I'm warning you.

41
00:03:34,761 --> 00:03:35,863
Why do you have a hot temper

42
00:03:35,863 --> 00:03:37,297
after coming back?

43
00:03:37,297 --> 00:03:38,465
What's the matter?

44
00:03:39,133 --> 00:03:41,735
Why is he treating me like this?

45
00:03:41,735 --> 00:03:43,971
We've been together for so long.

46
00:03:43,971 --> 00:03:45,272
Doesn't he understand me?

47
00:03:45,272 --> 00:03:46,807
Okay, okay. It's fine.

48
00:03:46,807 --> 00:03:48,976
Am I not making it clear enough?

49
00:03:48,976 --> 00:03:50,277
Let it go.

50
00:03:50,277 --> 00:03:51,645
Why can't he see it?

51
00:03:53,714 --> 00:03:55,282
I also want to know the reason.

52
00:03:55,749 --> 00:03:58,085
Is it because we are so close?

53
00:03:58,752 --> 00:03:59,553
What do you mean?

54
00:03:59,553 --> 00:04:00,420
Well.

55
00:04:00,921 --> 00:04:01,588
Check it out.

56
00:04:01,588 --> 00:04:04,191
When we are close,
I can't see you clearly.

57
00:04:04,191 --> 00:04:05,626
When we stay away from each other,

58
00:04:05,626 --> 00:04:07,628
I can see you clearly.

59
00:04:07,628 --> 00:04:09,062
When we are close,
I can't see you clearly.

60
00:04:09,062 --> 00:04:10,030
I can't see you clearly.

61
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:11,632
Now, I can see you clearly.

62
00:04:12,399 --> 00:04:14,134
So cute.

63
00:04:18,205 --> 00:04:19,173
I've looked for you for long.

64
00:04:19,173 --> 00:04:20,007
You're here.

65
00:04:23,343 --> 00:04:24,411
Come back with me.

66
00:04:24,411 --> 00:04:25,512
Where shall we go?

67
00:04:26,013 --> 00:04:27,814
I have nothing to do with you anymore.

68
00:04:27,814 --> 00:04:29,216
I don't live there anymore.
Let go of me.

69
00:04:29,917 --> 00:04:30,717
Are you going or not?

70
00:04:30,717 --> 00:04:31,752
I'm not going.

71
00:04:31,752 --> 00:04:32,686
Back then,

72
00:04:32,686 --> 00:04:34,000
Boss said this bar is mine.

73
00:04:34,563 --> 00:04:35,664
You are not welcome here!

74
00:04:35,664 --> 00:04:36,665
Get out!

75
00:04:38,366 --> 00:04:39,267
- Leave here!
- Get out!

76
00:04:40,001 --> 00:04:40,835
Leave here!

77
00:04:40,835 --> 00:04:42,170
- Hurry up!
- Turn off the music!

78
00:04:47,209 --> 00:04:48,443
Don't ever

79
00:04:48,443 --> 00:04:52,047
put mayonnaise on my fried egg again.

80
00:04:52,847 --> 00:04:54,316
That's the best way to enjoy it.

81
00:04:54,316 --> 00:04:56,218
Soy sauce is essential

82
00:04:56,218 --> 00:04:58,086
for a fried egg.

83
00:04:58,086 --> 00:04:59,421
Just like us.

84
00:04:59,854 --> 00:05:02,123
We're the perfect match,

85
00:05:02,123 --> 00:05:03,391
got it?

86
00:05:04,659 --> 00:05:05,727
After all this time together,

87
00:05:05,727 --> 00:05:07,495
how could you possibly not get it?

88
00:05:08,663 --> 00:05:09,798
Leave here!

89
00:05:11,466 --> 00:05:12,434
Naruto.

90
00:05:12,434 --> 00:05:13,568
What is that?

91
00:05:14,035 --> 00:05:16,171
Come here.

92
00:05:22,210 --> 00:05:23,545
Don't touch me!

93
00:05:23,545 --> 00:05:25,413
Do you think I'm an emotionless corpse?

94
00:05:25,981 --> 00:05:27,015
How do you feel?

95
00:05:35,991 --> 00:05:36,825
What do you want?

96
00:05:39,027 --> 00:05:39,761
I don't know.

97
00:05:41,863 --> 00:05:43,064
We've been friends since childhood,

98
00:05:43,064 --> 00:05:44,199
but I'm realizing how little

99
00:05:45,033 --> 00:05:45,867
I know about you.

100
00:05:47,068 --> 00:05:48,470
Is the man your ideal type?

101
00:05:50,905 --> 00:05:52,107
You actually let him hold you?

102
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,642
He was drunk.

103
00:05:54,676 --> 00:05:56,544
Didn't you notice he's taken?

104
00:05:56,978 --> 00:05:58,346
I'm also picky.

105
00:06:02,550 --> 00:06:03,385
What about me?

106
00:06:06,321 --> 00:06:07,989
Again. What's wrong with you?

107
00:06:08,857 --> 00:06:10,458
Can you just put it out of your mind?

108
00:06:10,458 --> 00:06:12,193
It's just about a night.

109
00:06:12,494 --> 00:06:14,396
Why did you enter prison
to protect Bai Zongyi?

110
00:06:16,197 --> 00:06:17,699
Because he is my friend.

111
00:06:18,133 --> 00:06:19,200
I knew someone was going to

112
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,935
hurt him, so of course
I'd try to help him.

113
00:06:21,903 --> 00:06:24,472
I was able to find that his attacker
was related to Fan Family.

114
00:06:24,472 --> 00:06:26,241
It's Fan Jiahong, Rui's third uncle.

115
00:06:26,241 --> 00:06:27,642
You're trying to
make amends for my fault?

116
00:06:30,845 --> 00:06:31,946
I'd had enough of it.

117
00:06:31,946 --> 00:06:33,048
Bai Zongyi is my friend.

118
00:06:33,048 --> 00:06:33,815
You are being stubborn.

119
00:06:35,417 --> 00:06:38,219
Besides, it's been four years since
the Zhang Teng incident was resolved.

120
00:06:38,687 --> 00:06:39,721
There's no point

121
00:06:39,721 --> 00:06:40,689
in bringing it up again now.

122
00:06:40,689 --> 00:06:41,756
It hasn't been resolved.

123
00:06:44,426 --> 00:06:45,460
What do you mean?

124
00:06:47,128 --> 00:06:48,697
There are still some issues.

125
00:06:50,465 --> 00:06:52,634
People associated with Zhang Teng

126
00:06:53,668 --> 00:06:55,403
have been disrupting my business lately.

127
00:06:59,474 --> 00:07:00,675
Can you help me?

128
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:09,951
Okay, I will help you.

129
00:07:10,151 --> 00:07:11,152
Can you leave then?

130
00:07:12,187 --> 00:07:13,688
I'll have someone
contact you if necessary.

131
00:07:14,956 --> 00:07:16,324
I want you to contact me personally.

132
00:07:17,158 --> 00:07:18,193
I'll just see you.

133
00:07:18,793 --> 00:07:20,161
I'll just answer your call.

134
00:07:20,161 --> 00:07:21,162
I'll only trust you.

135
00:07:24,499 --> 00:07:26,101
Okay.

136
00:07:26,101 --> 00:07:27,402
Got it. You can let go of me now.

137
00:07:29,104 --> 00:07:30,972
You should have hired
more henchmen so that

138
00:07:31,606 --> 00:07:33,541
there are people to take
the hit when shots are fired.

139
00:07:47,922 --> 00:07:48,923
Boss.

140
00:07:50,024 --> 00:07:52,394
Why are all the cakes
strawberry-flavored today?

141
00:07:52,694 --> 00:07:54,028
Today is strawberry day.

142
00:07:55,263 --> 00:07:56,965
Then give me a strawberry mille-feuille.

143
00:07:56,965 --> 00:07:57,499
Okay.

144
00:07:59,601 --> 00:08:01,202
Why is there a strawberry day?

145
00:08:01,202 --> 00:08:02,704
Is there a story behind it?

146
00:08:02,704 --> 00:08:03,671
Well.

147
00:08:04,205 --> 00:08:05,974
You're not doing this for…

148
00:08:07,509 --> 00:08:08,176
No.

149
00:08:08,176 --> 00:08:09,377
Oh no.

150
00:08:09,377 --> 00:08:11,079
I don't have a chance anymore, do I?

151
00:08:12,013 --> 00:08:12,614
Here you go.

152
00:08:12,881 --> 00:08:15,216
- Enjoy.
- Your partner is lucky.

153
00:08:19,187 --> 00:08:20,588
Here you are.

154
00:08:20,588 --> 00:08:22,357
Yeah.

155
00:08:24,392 --> 00:08:25,894
They are all strawberry-flavored?

156
00:08:26,394 --> 00:08:27,562
It's because of Rui, isn't it?

157
00:08:34,836 --> 00:08:35,603
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

158
00:08:38,106 --> 00:08:39,441
How do you feel about switching from

159
00:08:39,441 --> 00:08:40,375
being a doctor to a baker?

160
00:08:41,242 --> 00:08:42,343
What about you?

161
00:08:42,343 --> 00:08:43,978
After being carried away by Chen Yi...

162
00:08:45,346 --> 00:08:47,382
I came to Taichung specifically
to see you this time.

163
00:08:47,382 --> 00:08:48,817
Don't mention him.

164
00:08:56,124 --> 00:08:57,091
He said that Zhang Teng's men

165
00:08:57,091 --> 00:08:59,060
are still bitter about
the incident from four years ago.

166
00:09:00,295 --> 00:09:02,397
Sometimes they caused
trouble at his places.

167
00:09:04,199 --> 00:09:05,667
But don't worry.

168
00:09:05,667 --> 00:09:07,836
He has already sent someone
to protect your family.

169
00:09:07,836 --> 00:09:09,304
He won't make the same mistake again.

170
00:09:11,739 --> 00:09:13,107
It would be nice if I could forget.

171
00:09:14,209 --> 00:09:16,144
I'm still scared
when I think about it now.

172
00:09:17,278 --> 00:09:18,813
There's nothing you can do about it.

173
00:09:18,813 --> 00:09:21,049
Your injury can only affect
your current memory, so you can still

174
00:09:21,049 --> 00:09:22,684
remember every detail
from four years ago.

175
00:09:37,432 --> 00:09:39,167
Is that why you can't forget Rui?

176
00:09:40,902 --> 00:09:42,470
I don't want to forget Zherui.

177
00:09:44,239 --> 00:09:45,840
Why can you be so optimistic?

178
00:09:47,442 --> 00:09:49,010
I have to give myself hope.

179
00:09:49,677 --> 00:09:50,979
I have faith that

180
00:09:50,979 --> 00:09:52,113
he will remember me one day.

181
00:09:53,848 --> 00:09:54,949
He'll open this door

182
00:09:54,949 --> 00:09:56,050
and say,

183
00:09:56,050 --> 00:09:57,252
"I'm back."

184
00:10:04,359 --> 00:10:05,860
That's 735 in total.

185
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:08,062
Please come again if it's delicious.

186
00:10:15,637 --> 00:10:16,738
- I'm sorry.
- Sorry.

187
00:10:35,023 --> 00:10:36,024
Do you know him?

188
00:10:37,292 --> 00:10:38,293
No.

189
00:10:41,396 --> 00:10:42,830
Do we know each other?

190
00:10:44,299 --> 00:10:45,466
I mistook you for someone else.

191
00:10:47,268 --> 00:10:49,837
I mistook you for a friend. Sorry.

192
00:10:53,174 --> 00:10:55,109
We will be visiting Xuan'en Tech.

193
00:10:55,109 --> 00:10:56,945
Here is some background about them.

194
00:11:06,754 --> 00:11:07,922
Can we take the elevator first?

195
00:11:09,023 --> 00:11:10,325
Yeah. Sure.

196
00:11:41,389 --> 00:11:43,091
(In 2023,)

197
00:11:43,725 --> 00:11:45,293
(I ran across Zherui)

198
00:11:45,293 --> 00:11:46,127
(at Jiahong Trading.)

199
00:11:48,162 --> 00:11:49,163
(He's doing very well.)

200
00:11:51,165 --> 00:11:52,600
(His friend)

201
00:11:53,501 --> 00:11:54,702
(is also very kind to him.)

202
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,038
(He)

203
00:11:59,507 --> 00:12:00,441
(doesn't remember me.)

204
00:12:23,054 --> 00:12:29,337
(Zherui's album)

205
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,682
Zongyi, let's have late-night snack.

206
00:12:41,249 --> 00:12:42,016
Coming.

207
00:12:53,227 --> 00:12:54,162
