208
00:12:54,495 --> 00:12:56,798
The stir-fried cabbage Dad made
is very crispy and delicious.

209
00:12:56,798 --> 00:12:58,466
Come on, eat a little bit with us.

210
00:12:59,133 --> 00:13:00,935
You guys are so mean.

211
00:13:00,935 --> 00:13:03,004
