lead to weight gain.

212
00:13:03,337 --> 00:13:04,706
We just got off work.

213
00:13:04,706 --> 00:13:05,673
Eat a little bit with us.

214
00:13:05,973 --> 00:13:06,541
Come on.

215
00:13:07,141 --> 00:13:08,509
Only half a bowl.

216
00:13:09,143 --> 00:13:10,044
Just half a bowl.

217
00:13:10,678 --> 00:13:11,713
Okay, that's enough.

218
00:13:12,413 --> 00:13:13,047
Enough.

219
00:13:13,948 --> 00:13:15,049
Okay, half a bowl.

220
00:13:16,284 --> 00:13:17,785
Dad, look at him.

221
00:13:17,785 --> 00:13:19,320
Eating vegetables won't make you fat.

222
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,388
I worry that you will go hungry.

223
00:13:20,388 --> 00:13:22,123
Weight gain reduces fall pain.

224
00:13:22,123 --> 00:13:23,391
So annoying.

225
00:13:23,391 --> 00:13:24,792
Then I'll eat this braised pork.

226
00:13:25,626 --> 00:13:26,694
Aren't you not eating?

227
00:13:26,694 --> 00:13:28,296
You asked me to eat.

228
00:13:28,796 --> 00:13:29,964
Wasn't weight gain your concern?

229
00:13:31,699 --> 00:13:34,736
Did you know that chubby girls
are currently trending?

230
00:13:34,736 --> 00:13:36,170
Great, then eat more.

231
00:13:46,748 --> 00:13:47,415
Chen Yi is not here?

232
00:13:49,484 --> 00:13:50,752
Mr. Yi said he'll return shortly.

233
00:13:50,752 --> 00:13:51,919
Please wait for him.

234
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:54,122
Alright.

235
00:13:54,122 --> 00:13:54,989
Go ahead with your work.

236
00:13:55,957 --> 00:13:56,891
Yes.

237
00:14:02,163 --> 00:14:03,331
How have you

238
00:14:03,331 --> 00:14:04,365
all been doing lately?

239
00:14:05,366 --> 00:14:07,068
We're doing fine.

240
00:14:07,068 --> 00:14:08,202
Very fine.

241
00:14:10,438 --> 00:14:11,239
Leave.

242
00:14:11,239 --> 00:14:12,406
Thanks, Ai Di.

243
00:14:19,247 --> 00:14:20,448
There's definitely something wrong.

244
00:14:31,926 --> 00:14:34,195
When did he start littering
the house with items?

245
00:14:35,930 --> 00:14:36,964
He got bad.

246
00:15:10,431 --> 00:15:11,265
Chen Yi.

247
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:16,704
I smell blood.

248
00:15:22,643 --> 00:15:23,511
What's wrong with you?

249
00:15:26,214 --> 00:15:27,215
Just a minor injury.

250
00:15:27,782 --> 00:15:28,716
It will heal in a few days.

251
00:15:31,686 --> 00:15:33,054
Anyway, I come to tell you

252
00:15:33,788 --> 00:15:35,122
the Dragon Gang has entirely wiped out

253
00:15:35,122 --> 00:15:36,290
Zhang Teng's underlings.

254
00:15:36,924 --> 00:15:38,259
If it is genuinely about Zhang Teng,

255
00:15:38,259 --> 00:15:39,427
it should be his relatives.

256
00:15:42,129 --> 00:15:43,397
I plan to look into that further.

257
00:15:43,397 --> 00:15:43,998
What do you think?

258
00:15:45,867 --> 00:15:46,868
Speak up.

259
00:15:48,102 --> 00:15:49,070
You wouldn't act like this

260
00:15:49,070 --> 00:15:50,304
when I got close to you in the past.

261
00:15:51,205 --> 00:15:51,806
Why?

262
00:15:53,774 --> 00:15:55,009
It's none of your business.

263
00:15:58,045 --> 00:15:59,113
Do not leave without explaining.

264
00:16:04,185 --> 00:16:06,988
Multiple attempts have been made
by Fan family to harm Bai Zongyi.

265
00:16:07,622 --> 00:16:09,390
We will be killed
if we let our guard down.

266
00:16:11,392 --> 00:16:12,627
Come find me when you're serious

267
00:16:12,627 --> 00:16:13,661
about discussing Zhang Teng.

268
00:16:25,806 --> 00:16:26,874
What is it?

269
00:16:29,043 --> 00:16:31,045
You don't want to let me go?
You want to play with me?

270
00:16:34,782 --> 00:16:35,950
What?

271
00:16:38,619 --> 00:16:39,854
What if I said yes?

272
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:06,847
Chen Yi, what's wrong with you?

273
00:17:06,847 --> 00:17:07,982
Isn't it just for fun?

274
00:17:10,418 --> 00:17:11,519
Why are you suddenly afraid?

275
00:17:19,894 --> 00:17:21,195
I'm not interested right now.

276
00:17:22,063 --> 00:17:22,863
But I am.

277
00:17:27,935 --> 00:17:29,570
Can you face your favorite boss
if you do this?

278
00:17:29,570 --> 00:17:31,005
He is always the boss.

279
00:17:31,005 --> 00:17:32,373
The man who raised us.

280
00:17:33,774 --> 00:17:34,342
You're insane!

281
00:17:37,945 --> 00:17:38,980
Chen Yi.

282
00:17:44,618 --> 00:17:45,786
I don't know you well enough,

283
00:17:47,488 --> 00:17:48,723
but I do know

284
00:17:49,357 --> 00:17:52,059
that when you lie,
you pick at your pinky.

285
00:18:02,903 --> 00:18:03,904
I'll make it

286
00:18:04,405 --> 00:18:05,606
happen next time.

287
00:18:08,776 --> 00:18:09,777
You're crazy.

288
00:18:11,412 --> 00:18:12,713
I just figured it out, Ai Di.

289
00:18:13,414 --> 00:18:14,548
I'm serious.

290
00:18:16,183 --> 00:18:17,518
Get your wound treated.

291
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,495
Zongyi, let's play a game.

292
00:18:27,495 --> 00:18:29,163
The loser does the dishes.

293
00:18:29,163 --> 00:18:31,232
Sure, I'm all for it.

294
00:18:31,232 --> 00:18:33,167
Rock, paper, scissors.

295
00:18:33,768 --> 00:18:34,935
I won.

296
00:18:34,935 --> 00:18:36,771
You wash the dishes.

297
00:18:37,271 --> 00:18:39,607
It's a miracle
when the person you like also likes you.

298
00:18:40,808 --> 00:18:42,543
A miracle doesn't happen
just by hoping for it.

299
00:18:42,543 --> 00:18:44,111
You need to get off the car.

300
00:18:44,111 --> 00:18:45,212
And press the doorbell.

301
00:18:46,247 --> 00:18:47,915
Non-talkers shouldn't
start talking a lot.

302
00:18:50,017 --> 00:18:51,185
32 seconds.

303
00:18:52,219 --> 00:18:53,788
You could only hold so long
when you met him.

304
00:18:53,788 --> 00:18:54,922
What on earth do you want to do?

305
00:18:55,623 --> 00:18:56,791
Don't you want to know

306
00:18:56,791 --> 00:18:58,259
how Bai Zongyi currently
feels about you?

307
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,728
He seems fond of you.

308
00:19:01,695 --> 00:19:02,963
But your attitude...

309
00:19:02,963 --> 00:19:04,165
It's none of your business.

310
00:19:06,967 --> 00:19:08,235
Bai Zongyi doesn't blame you.

311
00:19:09,103 --> 00:19:10,638
The shop he has opened is proof of this.

312
00:19:10,638 --> 00:19:11,839
He's waiting for you.

313
00:19:14,608 --> 00:19:16,777
He would have been a great doctor.

314
00:19:17,878 --> 00:19:19,113
I ruined him.

315
00:19:23,851 --> 00:19:25,386
Deciding to fall in love with someone

316
00:19:25,386 --> 00:19:27,621
is akin to entrusting
your life to that person.

317
00:19:28,355 --> 00:19:29,757
Unless he doesn't love you,

318
00:19:29,757 --> 00:19:31,792
he will be yours for life.

319
00:19:33,794 --> 00:19:35,463
You only have one reason not to see him.

320
00:19:37,631 --> 00:19:38,699
You're scared.

321
00:19:51,378 --> 00:19:52,446
You won't see him?

322
00:19:54,148 --> 00:19:55,616
It's not time to see him yet.

323
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:00,554
You really don't mind

324
00:20:00,855 --> 00:20:02,022
if I exact my revenge on them?

325
00:20:03,257 --> 00:20:04,959
The only condition for your cooperation

326
00:20:04,959 --> 00:20:06,627
is that you are allowed to seek justice.

327
00:20:08,129 --> 00:20:09,330
I always keep my word.

328
00:20:10,197 --> 00:20:11,966
Even if it means sending them to jail?

329
00:20:13,734 --> 00:20:16,036
The Fan Family can handle
this humiliation.

330
00:20:37,925 --> 00:20:38,893
Welcome.

331
00:20:46,333 --> 00:20:48,335
Tell me what Chen Yi means.

332
00:20:49,637 --> 00:20:50,171
I have no idea

333
00:20:50,171 --> 00:20:51,739
what happened between you and Chen Yi.

334
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,175
Haven't I told you before?

335
00:20:55,943 --> 00:20:57,278
Right. You're forgetful.

336
00:20:57,278 --> 00:20:57,861
(Invoice)

337
00:20:58,812 --> 00:21:00,681
It's transient memory loss.

338
00:21:01,215 --> 00:21:03,284
That means you have a bad memory,
and it makes no difference.

339
00:21:05,486 --> 00:21:07,121
I grew up with him.

340
00:21:07,121 --> 00:21:08,122
Why on earth

341
00:21:08,122 --> 00:21:09,089
would he fall

342
00:21:09,089 --> 00:21:10,191
for an old man?

343
00:21:11,125 --> 00:21:12,560
He still likes the old man?

344
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:15,129
What you just said makes
it sound like that's not the case.

345
00:21:15,129 --> 00:21:16,197
You know it yourself, right?

346
00:21:17,831 --> 00:21:19,166
How would I know?

347
00:21:19,767 --> 00:21:22,136
You specifically came to Taichung
to show off to me, didn't you?

348
00:21:22,136 --> 00:21:23,837
You want to hear me say
that Chen Yi likes you.

349
00:21:25,072 --> 00:21:26,874
No way. Who cares?

350
00:21:27,474 --> 00:21:30,144
Having a bad memory
doesn't mean I'm stupid.

351
00:21:31,245 --> 00:21:32,346
No, I mean...

352
00:21:32,346 --> 00:21:33,948
The cheese has been refrigerated.

353
00:21:36,383 --> 00:21:37,418
You are…

354
00:21:38,519 --> 00:21:40,521
She is my high school classmate
who sat next to me.

355
00:21:41,422 --> 00:21:43,157
The one who kept following you around?

356
00:21:44,258 --> 00:21:45,125
How did you become so old?

357
00:21:45,125 --> 00:21:46,660
How come you haven't grown taller?

358
00:21:47,494 --> 00:21:48,295
Fine, you win.

359
00:21:49,997 --> 00:21:51,098
She works in your shop?

360
00:21:51,999 --> 00:21:53,167
Handle the store while I deliver.

361
00:21:53,701 --> 00:21:54,668
Be careful.

362
00:21:55,970 --> 00:21:57,871
Bai Zongyi, I'm not done talking.

363
00:21:57,871 --> 00:21:59,139
Just let me show off, okay?

364
00:22:05,346 --> 00:22:06,247
Bai Zongyi!

365
00:22:10,451 --> 00:22:11,919
Say it.

366
00:22:12,386 --> 00:22:13,921
You really think he likes me?

367
00:22:14,321 --> 00:22:15,322
Right?

368
00:22:15,889 --> 00:22:17,858
He wouldn't have
dragged me into bed otherwise.

369
00:22:18,559 --> 00:22:21,061
It's not appropriate
to talk about this in public.

370
00:22:21,462 --> 00:22:22,830
Tell me.

371
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:23,998
Just say it and I'll stop asking.

372
00:22:24,598 --> 00:22:26,066
Hurry up, or you'll forget later.

373
00:22:26,066 --> 00:22:27,001
I have to tell you again.

374
00:22:27,668 --> 00:22:28,402
Geez.

375
00:22:28,402 --> 00:22:30,371
Don't you know him better than I do?

376
00:22:31,739 --> 00:22:33,073
I'm just worried that I'm only seeing

377
00:22:33,073 --> 00:22:34,141
what I want to see.

378
00:22:35,409 --> 00:22:37,311
I wonder if you would have
the courage to seize a dream

379
00:22:37,311 --> 00:22:38,612
if it were suddenly presented to you.

380
00:22:46,654 --> 00:22:47,454
What?

381
00:22:48,355 --> 00:22:49,757
He doesn't remember us.

382
00:22:50,057 --> 00:22:51,625
Don't bother him.

383
00:22:51,625 --> 00:22:52,293
Oh, right.

384
00:22:52,793 --> 00:22:54,428
Mr. Hong's daughter is here,

385
00:22:54,428 --> 00:22:55,696
let's have dinner together.

386
00:23:06,407 --> 00:23:07,908
Let's go.

387
00:23:15,849 --> 00:23:17,084
You really don't do anything?

388
00:23:34,297 --> 00:23:37,148
(Promotional picture
of Bai Zongyi's cake shop)

389
00:23:37,237 --> 00:23:38,706
Are you sure
you don't want to go find him?

390
00:23:40,107 --> 00:23:41,975
We are leaving Taichung tomorrow.

391
00:23:44,545 --> 00:23:46,080
Can you really stand it?

392
00:24:13,807 --> 00:24:15,342
(Fan Zherui's memory loss is a lie.)

393
00:24:15,342 --> 00:24:16,910
(If you want to see him today, meet him)

394
00:24:16,910 --> 00:24:19,279
(at 10 p.m. in Room 703, Shengyu Hotel.)

395
00:24:23,671 --> 00:24:30,431
♪A rainy day, a dream♪

396
00:24:30,431 --> 00:24:37,215
♪A story restarts♪

397
00:24:37,215 --> 00:24:42,431
♪As I turn around♪

398
00:24:42,431 --> 00:24:47,231
♪My gaze lingers on you♪

399
00:24:47,231 --> 00:24:50,083
♪for a night♪

400
00:24:50,944 --> 00:24:52,045
Zherui.

401
00:25:07,507 --> 00:25:11,451
♪I can finally move on♪

402
00:25:11,451 --> 00:25:17,661
♪I gave up on you♪

403
00:25:17,661 --> 00:25:22,523
♪That place out of everyone's reach♪

404
00:25:22,523 --> 00:25:28,187
♪No need to say it, I know the answer♪

405
00:25:28,187 --> 00:25:33,284
♪This lost love I regained♪

406
00:25:33,284 --> 00:25:38,968
♪Tell me, how long will it last?♪

407
00:25:38,968 --> 00:25:43,714
♪My defense is on the verge of failing♪

408
00:25:43,716 --> 00:25:49,467
♪Yet I promised to never cry again♪

409
00:25:49,467 --> 00:25:53,851
♪So I am not good enough
to love you once more♪

410
00:25:53,851 --> 00:25:55,982
♪The distance between us♪

411
00:25:55,982 --> 00:25:59,771
♪Is like the sky and the ground,
it breaks my heart♪

412
00:25:59,771 --> 00:26:04,686
♪Could a cat fall in love with a mouse?♪

413
00:26:04,686 --> 00:26:06,587
♪I want to believe♪

414
00:26:06,587 --> 00:26:10,852
♪That it's always possible♪

415
00:26:10,852 --> 00:26:11,835
♪To have a miracle♪

416
00:26:11,835 --> 00:26:13,856
♪Ignore what they say♪

417
00:26:13,939 --> 00:26:14,873
You have to actively pursue

418
00:26:14,873 --> 00:26:16,875
the things you like.

419
00:26:17,876 --> 00:26:18,911
I don't even know why

420
00:26:18,911 --> 00:26:20,379
I like him so much.

421
00:26:22,681 --> 00:26:24,316
I only like him.

